Proposed law provides that all contributions to a portable benefit account are voluntary and
shall not be used as a criterion for determining an individual's employment classification.
Proposed law prohibits inferring contributions as evidence of an employer's liability and
prohibits a court from construing contributions as an element of an employment relationship
for any purpose under state workers' compensation and employment security laws.
